{"ts":"2026-06-27T02:50:08.752Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"xt450fi9","input":{"summary":"Successfully implemented the premium, custom frontend-only forgot password and OTP preview states inside the client portal login experience (`/components/portal/SecureLogin.tsx`). \n\n### Implementation Details:\n1. **Interactive Forgot Password (Passphrase Key Recovery) Flow**:\n   - Upgraded the existing modal to a multi-stage, state-driven workflow.\n   - **Form Stage**: Prompts for a registered enterprise email with robust HTML5 required-field validation.\n   - **Success Stage**: Upon mock request submission, a simulated handshake process is initiated. A high-fidelity sandbox dashboard displays detailed variables (deterministic SHA-like hash based on the email, sandbox-preview notice, and simulation vectors) alongside a clear and honest disclosure: *'NOTICE: Real password reset emails will be fully connected in the backend authentication phase.'*\n   - Includes full access keys and actions to easily return/reset.\n\n2. **Tailored OTP (Multi-Factor token code) Preview Component**:\n   - Replaced the simple static input with a premium, custom simulated multi-factor module.\n   - Restructured the input field using numeric constraints (`pattern`, `inputMode=\"numeric\"`, `maxLength={6}`), sanitizing keystrokes to ensure only numbers are accepted.\n   - Integrated dynamic warning states and honest microcopy detailing the UI-preview mode.\n   - Added accessible auxiliary action buttons: *'Generate Code'* (which populates the default `102486` token and streams the update to the terminal log), *'Clear'*, and *'Keycard Login'* (to toggle back methods cleanly).\n   - Validates on submission that the code is exactly 6 digits, showing localized inline cryptographic alerts if needed.\n\n3. **Engineering Integrity & Validation**:\n   - Both workflows push detailed live stream handshakes to the custom telemetry console log on-screen.\n   - Handled all responsive visual properties to match senior design parameters.\n   - Ran `npx eslint` and `npx tsc --noEmit` locally, with both reporting 100% clean builds without warnings or errors.\n   - Strictly followed the Landing Page continuity constraint (landing page remains untouched).","verified":true}}}
